<br>
metal rings till 40<br>
hooked arrow heads till 44<br>
pot till 50<br>
forged shuriken till 58<br>
lantern till 68<br>
dairy spoon till 74<br>
silver tiped arrowheads till 79<br>
banded mask till 90<br>
chain jointing till 95<br>
enchanted chain jointing till 106 if you can get a chanty to help ya or banded helm if not .. same triv<br>
enchanted metal rings till 115 again if a chanty will help ya, if not start on the ornate chain veil from here... <br>
<br>
